<?xml-stylesheet type="text/xsl" media="screen" href="/~d/styles/rss2full.xsl"?><?xml-stylesheet type="text/css" media="screen" href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~d/styles/itemcontent.css"?><rss xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/" xmlns:wfw="http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xmlns:sy="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/syndication/" xmlns:slash="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/" version="2.0"><channel><title>UNWIRE.HK</title><link>https://unwire.hk</link><description /><lastBuildDate>Wed, 15 Dec 2021 10:38:39 +0000</lastBuildDate><language>zh-TW</language><sy:updatePeriod>hourly	</sy:updatePeriod><sy:updateFrequency>1	</sy:updateFrequency><atom10:link xmlns:atom10="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml" href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/unwirelife" /><feedburner:info xmlns:feedburner="http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0" uri="unwirelife" /><atom10:link xmlns:atom10="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" rel="hub" href="http://pubsubhubbub.appspot.com/" /><item><title>【影評】《Spider-Man：No Way Home 蜘蛛俠：不戰無歸》     觀眾多次歡呼，現場氣氛媲美《END GAME》</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2021/12/15/spider-man-2/movie-2/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=spider-man-2</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[arthur]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Wed, 15 Dec 2021 10:23:37 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[城中熱話]]></category><category><![CDATA[電影 / 劇集]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1076194</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>小編每次寫影評都必要先說說，影評完全只是個人感受，人人都會有所不同，我說好看你可能會說很難看，不過這部《Spi [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>小編每次寫影評都必要先說說，影評完全只是個人感受，人人都會有所不同，我說好看你可能會說很難看，不過這部《Spider-Man：no way home 蜘蛛俠：不戰無歸》的影評，小編很有信心，影迷的感想都是一樣的，特別對於真正的蜘蛛俠影迷來說，看後大家都必會讚好，《Spider-Man：No Way Home》絕對是一部佳作，自《Avengers : END GAME》之後，最好看的一部 Marvel 電影。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/IMG_6234-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1076307" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/IMG_6234-1-384x580.jpg" alt="" width="384" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/IMG_6234-1-384x580.jpg 384w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/IMG_6234-1-596x900.jpg 596w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/IMG_6234-1-768x1160.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/IMG_6234-1-1017x1536.jpg 1017w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/IMG_6234-1.jpg 1059w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 384px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">Spider-man 買飛看 Spider-man 🙂</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/IMG_6238.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1076308" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/IMG_6238-383x580.jpg" alt="" width="383" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/IMG_6238-383x580.jpg 383w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/IMG_6238-595x900.jpg 595w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/IMG_6238-768x1162.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/IMG_6238-1015x1536.jpg 1015w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/IMG_6238.jpg 1057w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 383px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">叫他 Peter，立即給小編影相</p><p>寫這篇影評是比較有難度的，要完全不能劇透，但說多少少觀感就會很易劇透了，只能點到即止，小編也絕不想劇透，劇透會 XXX 的嘛。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/spider-man-new-trailer-blogroll-1636996700233-1639170097989.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1076298" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/spider-man-new-trailer-blogroll-1636996700233-1639170097989-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/spider-man-new-trailer-blogroll-1636996700233-1639170097989-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/spider-man-new-trailer-blogroll-1636996700233-1639170097989-1280x720.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/spider-man-new-trailer-blogroll-1636996700233-1639170097989-768x432.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/spider-man-new-trailer-blogroll-1636996700233-1639170097989-1536x864.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/spider-man-new-trailer-blogroll-1636996700233-1639170097989.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2>無冷場的緊湊情節</h2><p>《No Way Home》的情節承接著上一集《Far From Home》結尾，Spider-Man 被傳媒大肆報導為 Mysterio 的殺人兇手，真實身份及樣貌也被曝光，所以電影頭段已無冷場，情節已開始緊湊，而之後的劇情推進毫不拖泥帶水，每位反派的出場也是充滿著經典的味道及回憶的；而畫面方面，特技及打鬥也有高水準的表現，小編也極建議看 IMAX 版本。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/IMG_862.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1076297" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/IMG_862-694x287.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="287" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/IMG_862-694x287.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/IMG_862-768x318.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/IMG_862.jpg 1176w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/IMG_6226.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1076299" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/IMG_6226-268x580.png" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/IMG_6226-268x580.png 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/IMG_6226-416x900.png 416w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/IMG_6226-768x1663.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/IMG_6226-709x1536.png 709w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/IMG_6226-946x2048.png 946w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/IMG_6226.png 739w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">今朝的 IMAX 早場爆滿，身為蜘蛛俠 Fans 當然第一時間去看啦</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/IMG_6244-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1076303" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/IMG_6244-435x580.jpg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/IMG_6244-435x580.jpg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/IMG_6244-675x900.jpg 675w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/IMG_6244-768x1024.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/IMG_6244-1152x1536.jpg 1152w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/IMG_6244-1536x2048.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/IMG_6244-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">極建議去看 IMAX 版</p><h2>老戲骨的精湛演出</h2><p>雖然有那麼多《蜘蛛俠》過往的反派登場 (之前的電影預告及海報已全部亮相的了，這絕不是劇透啊)，但絕不會是一味的打打打的，文戲方面也安排得恰到好處，既有感人情節位，也有很多令人發笑的位，如果你是《蜘蛛俠》影迷，這近 20 年來都有看齊 Sony 及 Marvel 的《蜘蛛俠》電影，《No Way Home》的很多細節及對話，你都必定會感到很親切及感動，包你當年的回憶全部返晒來。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Spider-Man-No-Way-Home-Doc-Ock-Iron-Man-Upgrade.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1076311" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Spider-Man-No-Way-Home-Doc-Ock-Iron-Man-Upgrade-694x361.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="361" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Spider-Man-No-Way-Home-Doc-Ock-Iron-Man-Upgrade-694x361.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Spider-Man-No-Way-Home-Doc-Ock-Iron-Man-Upgrade-768x400.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Spider-Man-No-Way-Home-Doc-Ock-Iron-Man-Upgrade.jpg 960w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>另外值得留意的是老戲骨的精湛演出，例如扮演綠魔的 Willem Dafoe，他那奸到出汁的經典笑聲及樣子，令人難忘；而扮演八爪魚博士的 Alfred Molina，也寶刀未老，還是很有火的演技。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/willem-dafoe-900x506-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1076275" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/willem-dafoe-900x506-1-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/willem-dafoe-900x506-1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/willem-dafoe-900x506-1-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/willem-dafoe-900x506-1.jpg 900w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">當年奸到出汁的綠魔 (Willem Dafoe 飾演)</p><h2>片尾有兩個   片尾２既有驚喜又重要</h2><p>兩個片尾，而片尾二是更為有驚喜的，也是擺脫了 Marvel 式一般的片尾做法；而片尾二的其中一幕又是令到全場觀眾都歡呼大叫的。片尾２的劇情是 MCU 將來非常重要的鋪排，緊記要看啊！</p><p>自《Avengers : END GAME》以來，這部《Spider-Man：No Way Home》是唯一可以有如此有現場氣氛的電影，全場都是 Fans 的情況而又那麼有反應下看電影，實在是一件非常開心的事，希望不要再受到疫情的影響，這樣去戲院看電影才是一種享受。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/unnamed-2.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1076274" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/unnamed-2.jpg" alt="" width="356" height="512" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">自《Avengers : END GAME》以來，另一套現場氣氛那麼好的電影。</p><h2>入場前或重睇必看</h2><p>如果想對《蜘蛛俠》登場的所有奸角都有所認識，Netflix 現時已齊集了 Sony 出品的 5 部《蜘蛛俠》電影，可以入場前做定功課或重溫，入場看或重睇時必會有更深刻體會。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/IMG_861.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1076273" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/IMG_861-694x329.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="329" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/IMG_861-694x329.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/IMG_861-1280x606.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/IMG_861-768x364.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/IMG_861-1536x727.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/IMG_861.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p></p><div class="feedflare">
